Gays in the military is inevitable; lift ban sooner than later. Barry M. Goldwater. "Ban on Gays is Senseless Attempt to Stall the Inevitable" - "The country and the military know that eventually the ban will be lifted. The only remaining questions are how much muck we will all be dragged through, and how many brave Americans like Tom Paniccia and Margarethe Cammermeyer will have their lives and careers destroyed in a senseless attempt to stall the inevitable." 
